#: ../../C/careware.rst:9
msgid ""
"A variety of :ref:`shareware` for which either the author suggests that some"
" payment be made to a nominated charity or a levy directed to charity is "
"included on top of the distribution charge. Syn. : :ref:`charityware`\\; "
"compare :ref:`crippleware`\\, sense 2."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`shareware`\\ "
"の一種で、作者が指定の慈善団体への何らかの支払いを勧めるか、頒布料に上乗せして慈善団体向けの徴収金が含まれているもの。同義語は\\ "
":ref:`charityware`\\ 。\\ :ref:`crippleware`\\ の語義2と比較せよ。"
